item.description:
Here's a low key, great way to welcome in 2011 with your Baby Boomer friends.
We will first meet at 5p at the Atlantic Fish Company. After dinner, we'll check out the ice sculptures in Copley Square and around the Common. At 7p, we'll scope out great spots on Boylston to see the Parade. Dress warmly. The idea is to have an early night and be home way before midnight.
